The contents of this directory (specification/) are downloaded from
https://json-schema.org and https://github.com/json-schema-org/json-schema-spec.

Meta-schema JSON files are unmodified downloads. Human-readable spec
documents (*.md) are converted from the original HTML/PDF/text sources
into Markdown; content is preserved, formatting may differ from the
original.

